OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA rather cloudy day with
OL,6,Foccasional rain, heavy and thundery
OL,7,Frain at times. Some drier spells of
OL,8,Fweather too in the afternoon. Feeling
OL,9,Fwarm and humid.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FAny showers slowly dying out
OL,12,Fbut quite a cloudy evening in places
OL,13,Fwith some mist possible. Winds
OL,14,Fstrengthening overnight and feeling
OL,15,Fquite muggy and warm.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSaturday:FA cloudy start to the
OL,18,Fweekend, windy and feeling warm,
OL,19,Fsunshine breaking through in most
OL,20,Fareas. Perhaps some showers later in
OL,21,Fthe day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
